      },
      "date": "2013-08-09 14:10:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nHi Bob,\n\nI think there's a little more to do here.\n\nIn libcfs_ukuc_stop() let's set lk_wrd and lk_rfd to -1 after close. llapi_changelog_start() and llapi_hsm_copytool_register() both set lk_wfd to 0 after closing it.\n\nmdc_ioc_hsm_ct_start() has a CDEBUG() which prints lk_rfd using %d. I wonder how that gets past -Wformat.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
